      "role": "user",
      "content": "i understand the risk of clotting, but i've read online that some people actually do maintain their levels on much lower doses once they are stable. if i were to try the 2mg for a few weeks just to see how my body handles it, would that be a reasonable way to test if i can taper off? it feels like a much more proactive way to manage my health rather than just blindly taking the same amount forever.",
